Mplayer-m version 0.03
======================

A cool way for finding audio/video files and play with mplayer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  use File::Slurp
  use File::Find
  use List::MoreUtils
  use File::Basename

